---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import NomagicLogo from '../assets/nomagic.png';
---

<div class="h-full grid grid-cols-1 grid-rows-2">
    <div class="grid-rows-1 row-start-1">
        <div class="grid h-full grid-cols-2">
            <div class="h-full col-start-1 grid items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={NomagicLogo} alt="Nomagic" class="h-32 w-32"></Image>
            </div>
            <div class="h-full col-start-2 grid items-center justify-start">
                <ul class="space-y-8">
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://nomagic.ai/" target="_blank">
                        <h2 class="text-5xl hover:text-violet-500">Nomagic</h2>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h3 class="text-lg whitespace-pre-line">December 2022 - September 2023 &NewLine;(Part time)</h3>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-rows-1 row-start-2">
        <div class="h-full grid items-start justify-center place-content-start text-lg">
            <p>
                Worked as a Junior Robot Quality Assurance in Robotics industry. 
            </p>
            <p>
                The job involved handling evaluations prepared by ML engineers.
            </p> 
            <p>
                The tools used during my work were: Jenkins, Trello 
            </p>
            <p>
                Thanks to my performance I was sent for a secondment in Switzerland
            </p>
            <p>
                Where I worked in a production warehouse of the company client.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>